ter.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fpaul-weller-tickets%2Fartist%2F771145" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取剩余的美国门票，并访问<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fpaul-weller-tickets%2Fartist%2F771145" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>获取英国门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-paul-wellers-surprise-performance-outside-tiny-west-london-chip-shop-3776796">《观看保罗·韦勒 (Paul Weller) 在西伦敦小薯条店外的惊喜表演》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
